      <title>Milei 经济主管称阿根廷仍计划美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/argentina-still-plans-to-dollarize-milei-s-economy-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 经济部长表示，作为第一轮休克疗法的一部分，阿根廷比索大幅贬值后，他仍打算最终废除阿根廷比索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/argentina-still-plans-to-dollarize-milei-s-economy-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 02:56:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国钢铁产量将突破北京限制，三年来首次增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-s-steel-output-set-to-bust-cap-by-rising-for-first-time-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国钢铁产量有望实现三年来首次年度增长，因为经济问题优先于减少高污染行业排放的需要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-s-steel-output-set-to-bust-cap-by-rising-for-first-time-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 02:45:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大城市加大支持力度，中国房价进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-new-home-prices-fall-at-slower-pace-as-support-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国新房价格连续第六个月下跌，二级市场房价跌幅为九年来最大，凸显出当局正在加大力度应对房地产市场低迷的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-new-home-prices-fall-at-slower-pace-as-support-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 01:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行在经济困难之际提供创纪录的 1120 亿美元现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-expands-cash-coffers-with-13th-consecutive-loan-injection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于房地产市场低迷和需求疲软，中国经济增长复苏依然脆弱，中国以有史以来最大规模的中期政策贷款注入来扩大对经济的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-expands-cash-coffers-with-13th-consecutive-loan-injection</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 01:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
